Watch didn't mention sleep.

00:42:00.412 --> 00:42:02.120
To me, sleep is the
most interesting part

00:42:02.120 --> 00:42:03.670
of this little device.

00:42:03.670 --> 00:42:05.390
MEI-MEI ZHAO: Yeah, me too.

