Thanks.

00:45:25.690 --> 00:45:27.481
MEI-MEI ZHAO: Do you
find these days with--

00:45:28.080 --> 00:45:29.300
RICK SMOLAN: Everyone's
now taking pictures of me.

00:45:29.300 --> 00:45:31.175
MEI-MEI ZHAO: Everyone's
